data.description: One of few, custom built, brick ranch style homes on 3+ acres in Charlotte area.  This one conveniently located in the heart of Matthews. This home boasts beautiful brick work and archway windows  with a gorgeous courtyard space. This builder was ahead of his time, and displayed superior craftsmanship in the design and layout.  Solid core oak, double door welcomes you at the front entrance. Four spacious bedrooms, dining room and kitchen provide space and function needed in a home in prime location.  Beautiful brick carport attached and large enough for 2 cars. Detached, brick garage and additional shed convey with property. Home is VERY well built, and will need to be updated aesthetically.  Prime location in desirable Matthews near 74, 485, shopping, retail and all the conveniences of the beautiful town of Matthews, Mint Hill and Charlotte. Zoned R15 for residential and with proper approval can be subdivided. Sold AS-IS.
